        <h1>12-Week Workout Plan: Hypertrophy, Strength, and Power</h1>
        <p>This 12-week workout plan is divided into three 4-week phases: hypertrophy (muscle growth), strength, and power. Each phase adjusts the sets, reps, tempo, and rest periods to target specific goals while avoiding squats, deadlifts, and their variations. The plan follows a 5-day split, with neck and postural exercises integrated across the days to improve mobility, stability, and alignment.</p>
